            "draft_value": "* Restores stability to NASA Science with a $9 billion investment; ensures continued U.S. global leadership in space exploration.\n* Strategic response to rapid space science expansion by China; maintains U.S. leadership in setting norms for 21st-century exploration.\n* Protection of the aerospace industrial base; prevents further workforce layoffs and preserves critical technical capabilities.\n* Advancement of peer-reviewed Decadal Survey priorities; provides a nonpartisan, high-impact roadmap for scientific discovery.",
